    <item>
      <title>认知战中的验证成本不对称性：一个基于复杂性理论的框架</title>
      <link>https://qife122.github.io/p/%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E6%88%98%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E6%80%A7%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/</link>
